        "r2": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Richard",
            "verified": true,
            "date": "03/24/2026",
            "text": "My other half was diagnosed with a brain tumour a few years ago, resulting in surgery and radio/chemotherapy. She is now on various medications alongside the fear of serious seizures. KOPILOT.ID gives us piece of mind that regardless of which activity she is participating in, if anything happens someone can quickly find essential information."
          }
        },
        "r3": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Jerry",
            "verified": false,
            "date": "03/03/2026",
            "text": "What a great idea/product. I know this isn't the primary function, but I found a motorcycle helmet on the side of the interstate yesterday. I pulled over and grabbed it, and it had one of these tags on it. It says, \"Tap Phone Here\", so I did. It instantly pulled up the owner's info so I reached out to him and he got his helmet back. Again, not the main reason for having these things, but a great second-order benefit. And of course, the primary function of this tag (instant, on-scene access to medical and contact information) is vital, so I now have one on my motorcycle helmets and my skydiving helmets (cause…DUH !) ."
          }
        },
